image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a staircase landing inside a building. The stairs are carpeted in a dark grey grid pattern. A wooden handrail with blue metal balusters is on the left. On the wall at the landing, two fire extinguishers (one red, one black) are mounted. Above them is a sign that reads '5TH FLOOR'. There is a light fixture on the ceiling and a framed window or panel on the right wall.
image_analysis.layout: Interior architectural shot focusing on a stairwell landing and fire safety equipment.

document_metadata.subject: Interior photograph of building staircase and fire extinguishers

notes: The text '5TH FLOOR' is partially obscured by the fire extinguisher mounting bracket but remains legible. The identifier EFTA00001141 is a digital overlay typical of evidence or document production.
